# Import n8n Cloud Workflow

## Goal Description
The user wants to access and likely migrate/sync a workflow from n8n Cloud (`workflow/XFs5JLQeBeU80FFS`) to the local environment. Since direct browser access is blocked, we need to import the content manually.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Action Required**: Please export the workflow from `https://gonya90.app.n8n.cloud/workflow/XFs5JLQeBeU80FFS` as JSON and save it to a file (e.g., `cloud_workflow_import.json`) or paste the content.

